Package ca.mcgill.ecse211.dreamteamrobot.brick1.navigation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Location
    This object holds a coordinate.
    Navigator
    Navigator is a state machine running on a thread.
    ObstacleAvoider
    This is a sub-thread for a Navigator thread, which is run when Navigator determines that an obstacle is ahead.
    Odometer
    Odometer is a thread which uses the parameters in KinematicModel and changes in the tachometers of the left and right motors to estimate the robot's current position.
    OdometerCorrection
    Thread simultaneous to Odometer.
